name: nfoursid
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "nfoursid" %}
{% set version = "1.0.1" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: d481e8ad58f19eba4292498ea4fd1324572a31c776fe6cf2ca774ea42448c04b

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.7
  run:
    - python >=3.7
    - matplotlib-base >=3.3
    - numpy >=1.19
    - pandas >=1.1

test:
  imports:
    - nfoursid
    - nfoursid.tests
  requires:
    - pip
  commands:
    - python -m unittest discover -v nfoursid.tests

about:
  home: https://github.com/spmvg/nfoursid
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Implementation of N4SID, Kalman filtering and state-space models
  doc_url: https://nfoursid.readthedocs.io/en/latest/
  dev_url: https://github.com/spmvg/nfoursid

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - spmvg
